Quidditch match Gryffindor-Slytherin. Harry and Draco race to catch the Snitch, Draco throws Harry off his broom, he falls. He gets up, shakes himself off, takes a can of Sprite out of his pocket. Drinks. At this moment, the Snitch descends on his shoulder and flaps its wings. Harry with a satisfied look: - Quidditch is nothing, thirst is everything